      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Napoleon</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Chrono-partie-echecs-longwood.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0f/Chrono-partie-echecs-longwood.jpg/330px-Chrono-partie-echecs-longwood.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"238\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0f/Chrono-partie-echecs-longwood.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Chrono-partie-echecs-longwood.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Napoleon\">Napoleon</a> playing Chess with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henri_Gatien_Bertrand\">Bertrand</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Napoleon</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Pampaloni\" title=\"Marco Pampaloni\">Marco Pampaloni</a>, initialy written in <a href=\"/C_sharp\" title=\"C sharp\">C#</a> and soon re-written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a> and released in September 2013 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nNapoleon had its over the board tournament debut in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turin\">Turin</a> 2014, where it quite successfully participated at the <a href=\"/IGT_2014\" title=\"IGT 2014\">IGT 2014</a> becoming fourth with 4 out of 7. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Move_Generation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Move Generation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Transposition_Table\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Transposition Table</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-3 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Move_Ordering\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Move Ordering</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-3 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Selectivity\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selectivity</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-3 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Chess\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-3 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Games</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-15\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Move_Generation\"><a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Move Generation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Move_Generation#PseudoLegal\" title=\"Move Generation\">Pseudo-legal Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Encoding_Moves\" title=\"Encoding Moves\">16 Bit Move Encoding</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Transposition_Table\"><a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Transposition Table\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table#Bucket\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Four Bucket System</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table#ReplacementStrategies\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Depth-preferred Replacement Scheme</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Move_Ordering\"><a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Move Ordering\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation\" title=\"Principal Variation\">Principal Variation Extraction from TT</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV-LVA</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selectivity\"><a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Selectivity\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/AEL-Pruning\" title=\"AEL-Pruning\">AEL-Pruning</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning#AdaptiveNullMovePruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Adaptive Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning#Extendedfutilityprunning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Extended Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Razoring#LimitedRazoring\" title=\"Razoring\">Limited Razoring</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Adaptive Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Delta_Pruning\" title=\"Delta Pruning\">Delta Pruning</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> and more ...</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47996\">Aspiration windows</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Pampaloni\" title=\"Marco Pampaloni\">Marco Pampaloni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 14, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=50972\">Re: Napoleon PP by crybot - current edition</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Pampaloni\" title=\"Marco Pampaloni\">Marco Pampaloni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 21, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51656\">Tapered evaluation</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Pampaloni\" title=\"Marco Pampaloni\">Marco Pampaloni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 18, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51709\">Napoleon 1.4.0</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Pampaloni\" title=\"Marco Pampaloni\">Marco Pampaloni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 22, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53082\">Napoleon 1.5.0 64-bit Gauntlet for CCRL 40/40</a> by <a href=\"/Graham_Banks\" title=\"Graham Banks\">Graham Banks</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63926\">Parameter tuning with multi objective optimization</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Pampaloni\" title=\"Marco Pampaloni\">Marco Pampaloni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 07, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64390\">search efficiency</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Pampaloni\" title=\"Marco Pampaloni\">Marco Pampaloni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 23, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=64444\">Napoleon 1.8</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Pampaloni\" title=\"Marco Pampaloni\">Marco Pampaloni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 28, 2017</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crybot/Napoleon\">crybot/Napoleon · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crybot/Napoleon-old\">crybot/Napoleon-old · GitHub</a> (<a href=\"/C_sharp\" title=\"C sharp\">C#</a>)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.g-sei.org/napoleon/\">Napoleon</a> «&#160;<a href=\"/G_6\" title=\"G 6\">G 6</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerchess.org.uk/ccrl/404/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Napoleon&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">Napoleon</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL Blitz</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerchess.org.uk/ccrl/4040/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Napoleon&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">Napoleon </a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/15</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc_2\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Napoleon\">Napoleon from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Napoleon_%28disambiguation%29\">Napoleon (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Napoleone\">Napoleone from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Napoleon_of_India\">Napoleon of India from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.napoleon.org/en/home.asp\">Napoleon.org</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess\">Chess</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Napoleon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: Chess\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chesshistory.com/winter/extra/napoleon.html\">Napoleon Bonaparte and Chess</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_Winter_%28chess_historian%29\">Edward Winter</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.edochess.ca/batgirl/NapoleonChess.html\">Napoleon Bonaparte and Chess</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.edochess.ca/batgirl/welcome.html\">Sarah's Chess Journal</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/player/napoleon_bonaparte.html\">The chess games of Napoleon Bonaparte</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/index.html\">chessgames.com</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/perl/chessplayer?pid=77027\">The chess games of Madame de Remusat</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/index.html\">chessgames.com</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Napoleon_Opening\">Napoleon Opening from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scotch_Game#Analysis\">Napoleon Gambit</a> in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scotch_Game\">Scotch